@startuml SD08_Meteo_Dashboard

title SD08 — Meteo & Tableau de Bord

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 15
skinparam sequenceActorFontSize 15
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceParticipantPadding 15
skinparam sequenceActorPadding 10
skinparam ArrowThickness 2

actor "Utilisateur" as U
participant "App Mobile" as App
participant "weatherRoutes\n(Express)" as Weather
participant "irrigationRoutes\n(Express)" as IR
participant "fertilisationRoutes\n(Express)" as FR
participant "OpenWeather API" as OW
database "MongoDB" as DB

== Meteo actuelle ==

U -> App : Ouvre onglet "Meteo"
App -> Weather : GET /api/weather?city={ville}
Weather -> DB : Weather.findOne({ city })
alt Cache valide
  Weather --> App : meteo en cache
else Cache expire
  Weather -> OW : GET /data/2.5/weather
  Weather -> Weather : Calcul ET0 (Penman-Monteith FAO-56)
  Weather -> DB : Weather.create({ et0, ...data })
  Weather --> App : { et0, temperature, humidity, wind }
end
App --> U : Temperature, Humidite, Vent, ET0

== Previsions 5 jours ==

U -> App : Consulte previsions
App -> OW : GET /data/2.5/forecast?cnt=40
OW --> App : 40 entrees (3h/3h sur 5 jours)
App -> App : Groupe par jour (min/max temp)
App --> U : Previsions 5 jours

== Tableau de Bord ==

U -> App : Accede au tableau de bord
App -> Weather : GET /api/weather?city={ville}
Weather --> App : meteo + ET0
App -> IR : GET /api/irrigation/needs
IR --> App : { etcValues, volumes, nextIrrigDates }
App -> FR : GET /api/fertilisation
FR --> App : { prochaines echeances }
App --> U : Widget meteo + prochaines\nirrigations et fertilisations

== Recherche ville ==

U -> App : Saisit nom de ville
App -> OW : GET /data/2.5/weather?q={ville}
OW --> App : donnees ville
App --> U : Meteo mise a jour

@enduml